00:03:34,270 --> 00:03:36,310
Emperor Ying Yuan.

38
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,340
 Yan Dan. 

39
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:44,410
♫   I still have an image of you imprinted in my mind even after washing away the fine dust   ♫

40
00:03:44,410 --> 00:03:49,549
♫   Life after life, this is the longing I missed the most  ♫

41
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,700
You vile man,

42
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,900
come back quickly.

43
