When you're back,

44
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:07,460
I'll throw tiles with you.

45
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:12,420
And I'll lose to you on purpose to make you happy, okay?

46
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:22,780
And... And I haven't returned your cloak yet.

47
00:04:22,780 --> 00:04:25,740
