48
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:29,300
You promised me you would come back and watch it.

49
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:32,820
You're the Emperor. You must not break your promise.

50
00:04:32,820 --> 00:04:40,819
♫   You are the breeze of a fallen flower in the world of flowers adding to the mound of fallen flowers   ♫

51
00:04:40,819 --> 00:04:47,149
